## 🔒 Security Considerations

### **OTP Security:**
- ✅ 6-digit OTP (100,000 to 999,999)
- ✅ 5-minute expiry time
- ⏳ Max 3 attempts per OTP before requiring new one
- ⏳ Rate limiting: Max 1 OTP per minute per phone number
- ⏳ Track OTP attempts in database
- ⏳ Block suspicious activity (too many requests)

### **PIN Security:**
- ✅ SHA256 hashing (never plain text)
- ✅ 4-digit PIN (10,000 combinations)
- ⏳ Max 3 failed attempts before lockout
- ⏳ 15-minute lockout after 3 failures
- ⏳ Account lockout counter in database
- ⏳ PIN reset only via verified OTP
- ⏳ Notification on PIN change

### **Session Security:**
- ⏳ JWT tokens with 1-hour expiry
- ⏳ Refresh tokens for extended sessions (7 days)
- ⏳ Automatic logout after 15 minutes inactivity
- ⏳ Device-based session tracking
- ⏳ Ability to logout from all devices
- ⏳ Session history tracking

### **OAuth Security:**
- ⏳ Verify OAuth state parameter
- ⏳ PKCE flow for mobile apps
- ⏳ Validate redirect URIs
- ⏳ Check OAuth token expiry
- ⏳ Revoke tokens on logout

